Definition: a faint spot of light in the night sky that appears directly opposite the position of the sun
Example: a reflection of sunlight by micrometeoric material in space
Synonyms: gegenschein, light, a, faint, spot, of, in, the, night, sky, that, appears, directly, opposite, position, sun, reflection, sunlight, by, micrometeoric, material, space
Category: noun.phenomenon
